_sText:
General Info:
dm_castle_invasion_final took about 9 hours to create, texture, light, etc.. Making it the map I put the most time into. Also is the first map I've made with a 3d skybox.

Features:
- .nav file for bots
- 3d skybox
- Plenty of open space for movement, also enclosed areas for ambushes
- HDR available

Updates:
- Added HDR
- Optimized to fix the FPS drop when looking across the map
- Brightened the sun
- Added more lights
- Fixed the sewers
